# .NET Build Outputs
**/bin/
**/obj/

# Database
*.db
*.db-shm
*.db-wal

# IDE / Editor
.vs/
.vscode/
*.user
*.suo
.idea/

# Node / Angular
**/node_modules/
**/dist/
**/.angular/

# OS Files
Thumbs.db
.DS_Store

# Coverage & Test Results
**/coverage/
**/TestResults/

# Environment
.env.local
.env.production

# Logs
*.log
